(24463, 'Palenoid 0.1% topical gel 30 gm', 'بالينويد 0.1% جل موضعي 50جم', '9.75', '21', 'Adapalene', 'Zad', 'Gel', 'جل', '', 'Anti-acne', '0.1%', 'Adapalene is indicated for the topical treatment of acne vulgaris in patients aged 12 and over.[L12873] It is also indicated for acne vulgaris in combination with [benzoyl peroxide][L12930] and in a triple combination therapy with benzoyl peroxide and [clindamycin].[L48666]', '', '', 849, '2024-12-12', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
